	      <td class="curr" style="width: 1.5em; padding-right: 3em; border-bottom: double black;">6</td>
	    </tr>
               <tr>
	      <td class="par" colspan="2">Fifteen Companies at the same Rate only in Regard to the Difference between the Field Officers &amp; Captains, but that included the Pay for the 20 Companies with all the Commissioned Officers amounts <img class="char" src="images/char-per-trans.png" alt="[per]"/> Annum to</td>
	      <td style="vertical-align: top;" class="brace" rowspan="3"><img src="images/brace-close-trans.png" alt="}" class="brace" style="height: 3.5em; width: 17px;"/></td>
	      <td class="curr punc" style="padding-right: 0; vertical-align: middle;">33,561.</td>
	      <td class="curr punc" style="padding-right: 0; vertical-align: middle;">10.</td>
